---
layout: default
title: Blog
description: Thoughts on design, development, and building products
---

<div class="container">
  <section class="blog-intro">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-secondary mb-8">
      Thoughts on design, development, and building better products.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="blog-item">
      <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p class="text-secondary text-sm">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
      {% if post.data.description %}
      <p class="text-secondary">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
</div>